    <title>(已解决)微软商店遇到错误其中一个更新服务未正常运行,代码:0x80070424</title>
    <link href="https://yumi1.top/2023/08/22/windows-poser-1/"/>
    <id>https://yumi1.top/2023/08/22/windows-poser-1/</id>
    <published>2023-08-22T04:50:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-08-22T15:15:56.388Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="电脑信息"><a href="#电脑信息" class="headerlink" title="电脑信息"></a>电脑信息</h2><ul><li>型号    惠普 Victus by HP Laptop 16-d1XXX</li><li>系统     Windows 11 家庭版 Build 22000</li><li>cpu     12th Gen Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-12700H</li></ul><h2 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>发现微软商店无法打开,提示其中一个更新服务未正常运行,代码:0x80070424<br><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img" src="/image/store.png"/></div></div><br><i class="fa-brands fa-windows"></i> + <kbd>R</kbd>输入 <code>cmd</code>  运行</p><pre><code>WSReset.exe</code></pre><ul><li>重置商店无效</li><li>设置中运行疑难解答无效</li><li>运行sfc扫描</li></ul><p><i class="fa-brands fa-windows"></i> + <kbd>X</kbd> windows终端 管理员身份运行</p><pre><code>sfc /scannow</code></pre><ul><li>运行DISM扫描</li></ul><pre><code>DISM.exe /Online /Cleanup-image /Scanhealth # 扫描你全部系统文件并和官方系统文件对比DISM.exe /Online /Cleanup-image /Restorehealth # 把那些不同的系统文件还原成系统官方源文件，跟重装差不多</code></pre><p>这时参考<a href="https://www.thewindowsclub.com/windows-update-keeps-disabling-itself-automatically">Windows Update keeps disabling itself automatically in Windows 11/10</a>和<a href="https://www.thewindowsclub.com/what-is-clean-boot-state-in-windows">How to perform Clean Boot in Windows 11/10</a><br>发现是Windows Update服务无法正常启动</p><h2 id="解决方法"><a href="#解决方法" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h2><span class='p logo h1'>通过注册表编辑器手动恢复 Windows Update 服务</span><h3 id="打开注册表编辑器"><a href="#打开注册表编辑器" class="headerlink" title="打开注册表编辑器"></a>打开注册表编辑器</h3><p><i class="fa-brands fa-windows"></i> + <kbd>R</kbd>输入 <code>regedit</code> 运行</p><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img" src="/image/reg3.png"/></div></div><h3 id="找到计算机-HKEY-LOCAL-MACHINE-SYSTEM-CurrentControlSet-Services路径"><a href="#找到计算机-HKEY-LOCAL-MACHINE-SYSTEM-CurrentControlSet-Services路径" class="headerlink" title="找到计算机\HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services路径"></a>找到<code>计算机\HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services</code>路径</h3><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img" src="/image/reg.png"/></div></div><h3 id="找到wuauserv项-如果没有则跳到"><a href="#找到wuauserv项-如果没有则跳到" class="headerlink" title="找到wuauserv项,如果没有则跳到"></a>找到<code>wuauserv</code>项,如果没有则跳到</h3><p>右键<code>wuauserv</code>项,选择<code>导出</code>以备份<br><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img" src="/image/reg2.png"/></div></div><br>右键<code>wuauserv</code>项,选择<code>删除</code></p><h3 id="桌面新建一个文本文档"><a href="#桌面新建一个文本文档" class="headerlink" title="桌面新建一个文本文档"></a>桌面新建一个文本文档</h3><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img" src="/image/wbwd.png"/></div></div><p>复制以下代码到文本文档中,<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span 